               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoners Defence.</hi> I occupied the house at 76, Tower Street, and Jet out a great part of it, and the party who had taken that room bad gone away and left a lot of rent—the things were left in the room which the constable found and I tried to get money on them, to pay the rent I am not connected with the burglary. I never was near the place.</p>
